    <h1>Cancellation Policy</h1>



     



    <h2>1. Introduction</h2>



    <p>We understand that plans can change, and we strive to accommodate cancellations and modifications as best as we can. This policy outlines the terms and conditions for cancelling your travel arrangements with Bhraman.</p>



     



    <h2>2. Cancellation by the Traveler</h2>



    <ul>



      <li>If you cancel your booking more than 30 days before the departure date, you will receive a full refund minus any non-refundable deposits.</li>



      <li>If you cancel between 7 and 30 days before the departure date, you will receive a 50% refund.</li>



      <li>If you cancel less than 7 days before the departure date, no refund will be issued.</li>



    </ul>



     



    <h2>3. Cancellation by Bhraman</h2>



    <p>In rare cases, we may need to cancel a trip due to unforeseen circumstances such as natural disasters, political instability, or low enrollment. In such cases, you will receive a full refund or the option to reschedule your trip.</p>



     



    <h2>4. Modifications to Bookings</h2>



    <p>If you need to modify your booking, please contact us as soon as possible. While we will do our best to accommodate changes, modifications are subject to availability and may incur additional fees.</p>



     



    <h2>5. Refund Process</h2>



    <p>Refunds will be processed within 14 business days of receiving your cancellation request. The refund will be issued using the original payment method.</p>



     



    <h2>6. Contact Us</h2>



    <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, please contact our customer service team at <a href="mailto:support@bhraman.com">support@bhraman.com</a>.</p>



